@startuml Sequence_Spin
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam maxMessageSize 200

title **BIỂU ĐỒ TUẦN TỰ - QUAY SPIN WHEEL**

actor "Người dùng" as User #LightGreen
participant "Trang Spin\n(/spin)" as SpinPage #E3F2FD
participant "SpinWheel\nComponent" as Wheel #FFF3E0
participant "API Client\n(Axios)" as API #FCE4EC
participant "DecisionController" as Controller #E8F5E9
participant "DecisionService" as Service #C8E6C9
database "MongoDB" as DB #F3E5F5

== Bước 1: Tải trang Spin ==

User -> SpinPage : Truy cập /spin
activate SpinPage

SpinPage -> API : GET /api/categories
activate API
API -> Controller : request
activate Controller
Controller -> DB : Category.find({...})
activate DB
DB --> Controller : categories[]
deactivate DB
Controller --> API : {success: true, data: categories}
deactivate Controller
API --> SpinPage : categories[]
deactivate API

SpinPage --> User : Hiển thị dropdown\ndanh mục
deactivate SpinPage

== Bước 2: Chọn danh mục & tải choices ==

User -> SpinPage : Chọn danh mục "Đồ ăn"
activate SpinPage

SpinPage -> API : GET /api/categories/:id/choices
activate API
API -> DB : Choice.find({categoryId, isActive: true})
activate DB
DB --> API : choices[]
deactivate DB
API --> SpinPage : choices[]
deactivate API

SpinPage -> Wheel : render(choices)
activate Wheel
Wheel -> Wheel : Canvas API:\nVẽ vòng tròn\nChia segments\nGắn label + màu
Wheel --> User : Hiển thị vòng quay\nvới các lựa chọn
deactivate Wheel
deactivate SpinPage

== Bước 3: Quay Spin ==

User -> SpinPage : Nhấn "QUAY NGAY!"
activate SpinPage

SpinPage -> API : POST /api/decisions/spin\n{categoryId, question:\n"Ăn gì hôm nay?"}
activate API

API -> Controller : spin(req, res)
activate Controller

Controller -> Service : spin(userId, categoryId, question)
activate Service

== Thuật toán Smart Random ==

Service -> DB : Choice.find({categoryId,\nisActive: true})
activate DB
DB --> Service : activeChoices[]
deactivate DB

group Smart Random Algorithm
  Service -> Service : **Bước 1:** Lấy weight gốc\ncủa mỗi choice (1-10)
  Service -> Service : **Bước 2:** Nếu lastSelectedAt\n< 3 ngày → weight *= 0.5
  Service -> Service : **Bước 3:** Nếu timesSelected\n== 0 → weight *= 1.5
  Service -> Service : **Bước 4:** totalWeight =\nSUM(all weights)
  Service -> Service : **Bước 5:** random =\nMath.random() * totalWeight
  Service -> Service : **Bước 6:** Duyệt choices,\ncộng dồn → chọn winner
end

Service -> DB : Choice.findByIdAndUpdate(\nwinnerChoiceId, {\n  $inc: {timesSelected: 1},\n  lastSelectedAt: new Date()\n})
activate DB
DB --> Service : updated choice
deactivate DB

Service -> DB : Decision.create({\n  userId, categoryId,\n  choiceId: winner._id,\n  question,\n  status: "pending",\n  expiresAt: now + 24h\n})
activate DB
DB --> Service : new decision
deactivate DB

Service -> DB : UserStreak.findOneAndUpdate(\n  {userId},\n  {$inc: {totalDecisions: 1}},\n  {upsert: true}\n)
activate DB
DB --> Service : streak updated
deactivate DB

Service --> Controller : {decision, choice}
deactivate Service

Controller --> API : 201 Created\n{success: true, data: {decision}}
deactivate Controller

API --> SpinPage : decision with choice details
deactivate API

== Bước 4: Animation quay ==

SpinPage -> Wheel : startSpin(winnerIndex)
activate Wheel

Wheel -> Wheel : Tính góc quay:\nbaseRotation = 360° * 5 vòng\n+ góc đến winner segment

loop Animation 4 giây
  Wheel -> Wheel : requestAnimationFrame()\nCubic easing deceleration\nTick sound effect
end

Wheel -> Wheel : Dừng tại winner\nConfetti animation 🎉

Wheel --> SpinPage : onSpinComplete(result)
deactivate Wheel

== Bước 5: Hiển thị kết quả ==

SpinPage --> User : Modal kết quả:\n🍜 "Bún bò Huế"\n⭐⭐⭐⭐☆ $$\n[Chấp nhận] [Quay lại]

== Bước 6a: Chấp nhận ==

User -> SpinPage : Nhấn "Chấp nhận"

SpinPage -> API : PUT /api/decisions/:id/accept
activate API
API -> DB : Decision.findByIdAndUpdate(\nid, {status: "pending"})
activate DB
DB --> API : updated
deactivate DB
API --> SpinPage : {success: true}
deactivate API

SpinPage --> User : Redirect → /dashboard\n"Nhiệm vụ đã được ghi nhận!"
deactivate SpinPage

note over User, DB
  **Hoặc Bước 6b: Quay lại (Re-spin)**
  - Kiểm tra số lượt re-spin (tối đa 2/ngày)
  - Nếu còn lượt → spinCount++ → quay lại Bước 3
  - Nếu hết lượt → thông báo "Đã hết lượt quay lại"
end note

@enduml
